The paper discusses a solution for scalable computation in blockchains, which involves a financial incentive layer and a dispute resolution layer in the form of a verification game. This suggests that the paper could fall under the categories of cryptography (cs.CR), distributed computing (cs.DC), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), cybersecurity (cs.CY), or social and information networks (cs.SI).
